<p>For the third day in a row, I rode Flagstaff at lunch.  I was joined for the first section by Dave, but he had to split for a 1p presentation.  I think "The Hole" pretty much constitutes a Flagstaff ride by itself.</p>
<p>Given my Flagstaff hat-trick, I might as well go for broke and do it tomorrow and Friday&mdash;though the weather tomorrow might present a challenge.  I suppose I can always do a duathlon.  Hope you can join.</p>
